snippet.title: Throne and Liberty - Official Release Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Throne and Liberty is a free-to-play MMO fantasy RPG developed by NCSoft. Players will battle malevolent enemies and harness ancient powers to protect Solisium. Wield a diverse array of weapons, explore the dynamic and ever-changing open world, and customize the playable character to the exact specifications desired. Throne and Liberty is lanching on September 17 for PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC (Steam) on September 17 with an open beta running from July 18 - 23.

#IGN #Gaming
